1
00:00:00,020 --> 00:00:05,080
♪ Inside the state a city is built ♪

2
00:00:05,080 --> 00:00:10,190
♪ Where a benevolent emperor resides ♪

3
00:00:10,190 --> 00:00:15,330
♪ Court officials are brave and able ♪

4
00:00:15,330 --> 00:00:22,750
♪ The empress is fair ♪

5
00:00:25,580 --> 00:00:30,710
♪ Princes died too young to ascend the throne ♪

6
00:00:30,710 --> 00:00:35,570
♪ Princesses are spoiled and fragile ♪

7
00:00:35,840 --> 00:00:40,270
♪ Commoners are also the emperor’s children ♪

8
00:00:40,830 --> 00:00:49,630
♪ All are living peacefully ♪

9
00:00:49,930 --> 00:00:54,280
♪ Wish I could live a day for myself ♪

10
00:00:55,000 --> 00:00:59,380
♪ Follow my heart and ethics without distractions ♪

11
00:01:00,710 --> 00:01:03,400
♪ To be a good husband ♪

12
00:01:03,400 --> 00:01:05,970
♪ To be a caring father ♪

13
00:01:06,460 --> 00:01:10,110
♪ We were close when we first met ♪

14
00:01:10,460 --> 00:01:14,710
♪ I hope I can control my desires ♪

15
00:01:15,540 --> 00:01:20,060
♪ To be a worriless emperor and father ♪

16
00:01:21,120 --> 00:01:23,860
♪ Prudence tops all virtues ♪

17
00:01:23,860 --> 00:01:26,480
♪ People build the state ♪

18
00:01:26,750 --> 00:01:30,020
= Held in the Lonely Castle =
♪ May the world be peaceful ♪

19
00:01:30,020 --> 00:01:33,020
= Episode 53 =

20
00:01:33,780 --> 00:01:36,300
Fu Bi was ordered to welcome Khitan delegation

21
00:01:36,300 --> 00:01:37,740
that came for Qianyuan Festival.

22
00:01:38,100 --> 00:01:39,660
He found a young official,

23
00:01:39,660 --> 00:01:40,860
surnamed Xiao,

24
00:01:40,860 --> 00:01:42,660
who behaved abnormally

25
00:01:42,780 --> 00:01:44,260
against the reported list.

26
00:01:44,740 --> 00:01:46,500
Then Fu Bi sent a letter.

27
00:01:47,620 --> 00:01:48,980
Imperial Security Agency and Privy Council

28
00:01:49,140 --> 00:01:50,580
contacted emissaries in Khitan

29
00:01:51,100 --> 00:01:52,900
and confirmed that

30
00:01:52,900 --> 00:01:54,220
the man wasn’t an ordinary official,

31
00:01:54,340 --> 00:01:56,220
but the crown prince of Khitan,

32
00:01:56,620 --> 00:01:57,620
Yelv Hongji.

33
00:01:58,900 --> 00:02:00,380
Fu Bi visited Khitan as an envoy many times

34
00:02:01,100 --> 00:02:02,940
and knew a lot about local customs.

35
00:02:03,820 --> 00:02:05,740
And he’s always acute and careful.

36
00:02:07,020 --> 00:02:07,940
The crown prince

37
00:02:07,940 --> 00:02:10,060
is a mere young man of 16 to 17.

38
00:02:10,220 --> 00:02:11,260
He can’t fool Fu Bi.

39
00:02:14,340 --> 00:02:15,380
It’s been three years

40
00:02:15,380 --> 00:02:16,460
since I met Fu Bi.

41
00:02:16,460 --> 00:02:17,340
Speaking of him,

42
00:02:17,860 --> 00:02:18,740
his eldest daughter

43
00:02:18,780 --> 00:02:20,620
is old enough to get married.

44
00:02:21,620 --> 00:02:22,980
I have someone to introduce to her.

45
00:02:23,700 --> 00:02:25,020
I’d like to be their matchmaker.

46
00:02:25,540 --> 00:02:27,020
= Wen Yanbo, courtesy name Kuanfu =

47
00:02:27,020 --> 00:02:30,020
No one knows

48
00:02:30,820 --> 00:02:32,700
= Pang Ji, courtesy name Chunzhi =
why the crown prince is in the delegation.

49
00:02:33,700 --> 00:02:34,820
The delegation has the chance to meet you

50
00:02:35,380 --> 00:02:37,900
at Qianyuan Festival.

51
00:02:38,340 --> 00:02:40,780
I think Imperial Guards

52
00:02:41,340 --> 00:02:42,820
should be carefully checked again.

53
00:02:43,540 --> 00:02:44,660
The coup before the new year

54
00:02:45,100 --> 00:02:46,900
still makes me uneasy.

55
00:02:48,420 --> 00:02:49,940
Imperial Security Agency and Privy Council

56
00:02:50,180 --> 00:02:51,380
have emissaries in Khitan.

57
00:02:51,980 --> 00:02:53,060
Did they say

58
00:02:53,060 --> 00:02:56,500
the crown prince had great martial arts

59
00:02:56,500 --> 00:02:57,460
or super power?

60
00:02:58,060 --> 00:02:59,220
No.

61
00:02:59,580 --> 00:03:00,740
According to emissaries,

62
00:03:00,900 --> 00:03:02,740
the crown prince is very smart.

63
00:03:02,740 --> 00:03:04,460
He likes music and literature.

64
00:03:05,820 --> 00:03:08,020
But not all their news

65
00:03:08,140 --> 00:03:09,500
can be true.

66
00:03:10,300 --> 00:03:11,500
For such an important matter,

67
00:03:11,780 --> 00:03:14,380
we must take careful precautions.

68
00:03:16,620 --> 00:03:17,700
You invited us

69
00:03:17,700 --> 00:03:19,220
to come and enjoy your flower arrangement.

70
00:03:20,540 --> 00:03:21,340
Where is it?

71
00:03:22,660 --> 00:03:23,460
Don’t rush.

72
00:03:24,300 --> 00:03:25,380
Father promised me that

73
00:03:26,900 --> 00:03:27,860
he would come today.

74
00:03:29,140 --> 00:03:30,060
Her Highness has arrived.

75
00:03:38,580 --> 00:03:40,500
Huirou said she learnt flower arrangement secretly

76
00:03:40,700 --> 00:03:41,940
and asked me to enjoy it with Qiuhe.

77
00:03:43,620 --> 00:03:44,420
Where is it?

78
00:03:44,940 --> 00:03:45,700
I never saw her

79
00:03:45,700 --> 00:03:47,180
learn flower arrangement so carefully.

80
00:03:48,500 --> 00:03:50,660
I’m doing differently from others.

81
00:03:51,100 --> 00:03:52,300
I haven’t practiced much,

82
00:03:52,580 --> 00:03:53,980
but I made some original arrangement.

83
00:03:54,860 --> 00:03:56,340
She’s talking nonsense again.

84
00:03:58,460 --> 00:04:01,540
This disobeys the seventh diplomatic etiquette.

85
00:04:01,580 --> 00:04:02,420
All right.

86
00:04:04,220 --> 00:04:06,500
Yelv Hongji violated seven etiquettes,

87
00:04:06,940 --> 00:04:08,940
because of being disguised as an envoy.

88
00:04:09,140 --> 00:04:09,820
That’s enough.

89
00:04:10,420 --> 00:04:12,540
So, what do you think?

90
00:04:13,300 --> 00:04:15,740
Shall we ask Fu Bi to expose him

91
00:04:16,060 --> 00:04:17,140
and reprimand him

92
00:04:17,620 --> 00:04:19,180
or shall we send an official letter

93
00:04:19,180 --> 00:04:20,460
to Khitan master Zong Zhen

94
00:04:20,620 --> 00:04:21,940
for the punishment

95
00:04:22,460 --> 00:04:23,980
after he comes all the way to the Capital

96
00:04:24,340 --> 00:04:25,380
and further violates etiquette?

97
00:04:26,180 --> 00:04:27,260
We think

98
00:04:28,020 --> 00:04:30,060
Yuanhao just died.

99
00:04:30,260 --> 00:04:31,420
Situation in Xixia isn’t stable.

100
00:04:31,980 --> 00:04:34,340
Khitan people are enemies to Xixia people.

101
00:04:34,620 --> 00:04:35,900
They have frequent wars.

102
00:04:36,100 --> 00:04:37,740
They won’t form an alliance.

103
00:04:38,460 --> 00:04:41,220
We can detain the crown prince,

104
00:04:41,340 --> 00:04:42,500
for his violating diplomatic etiquettes

105
00:04:43,020 --> 00:04:45,660
and negotiate with Zong Zhen on border trade.

106
00:04:46,740 --> 00:04:47,420
Yeah.

107
00:04:48,060 --> 00:04:48,980
In recent years,

108
00:04:49,100 --> 00:04:51,900
Zong Zhen has given harsh conditions

109
00:04:52,260 --> 00:04:55,340
= Song Xiang, courtesy name Gongxu =
on selling war horses to us.

110
00:04:56,140 --> 00:04:58,860
It’s a good chance to negotiate on that.

111
00:05:01,540 --> 00:05:03,340
I understand what you mean.

112
00:05:04,180 --> 00:05:07,420
Let me think about it.

113
00:05:10,540 --> 00:05:11,370
His Majesty has arrived.

114
00:05:21,900 --> 00:05:22,700
You’re all here?

115
00:05:24,900 --> 00:05:25,660
Huirou.

116
00:05:26,300 --> 00:05:27,780
What have you done?

117
00:05:28,500 --> 00:05:29,740
What treasure do you have

118
00:05:29,740 --> 00:05:31,540
to show everyone here?

119
00:05:32,780 --> 00:05:33,700
Go get me

120
00:05:33,700 --> 00:05:35,380
the white plums I picked this morning.

121
00:05:51,820 --> 00:05:52,620
Hurry.

122
00:06:00,740 --> 00:06:02,020
Nice white plums.

123
00:06:03,340 --> 00:06:05,100
But the vases don’t match.

124
00:06:05,980 --> 00:06:07,420
Look at the flowers and the vases.

125
00:06:07,420 --> 00:06:08,420
They’re all white,

126
00:06:08,580 --> 00:06:09,860
but of different hues.

127
00:06:10,100 --> 00:06:11,340
The whiter the flowers are,

128
00:06:11,340 --> 00:06:12,820
the dirtier the vases look.

129
00:06:13,500 --> 00:06:14,540
There’s even a breach.

130
00:06:16,300 --> 00:06:17,220
Looks so bad.

131
00:06:18,380 --> 00:06:19,580
You said you learnt flower arrangement.

132
00:06:20,100 --> 00:06:21,700
I knew you weren’t patient enough.

133
00:06:22,620 --> 00:06:24,580
What other vases do I have?

134
00:06:25,100 --> 00:06:25,940
Father, you have

135
00:06:25,940 --> 00:06:27,340
an excellent red porcelain vase from Dingzhou.

136
00:06:27,660 --> 00:06:28,540
But you don’t give it to me.

137
00:06:29,660 --> 00:06:30,460
Why do you think

138
00:06:30,460 --> 00:06:31,460
I have a red porcelain vase?

139
00:06:32,020 --> 00:06:33,060
You always visited my chamber.

140
00:06:33,500 --> 00:06:34,860
Have you ever seen one?

141
00:06:35,900 --> 00:06:37,020
You don’t have any.

142
00:06:37,180 --> 00:06:38,460
But Noble Consort Zhang has it.

143
00:06:39,300 --> 00:06:40,220
Father, you showed partiality.

144
00:06:40,580 --> 00:06:42,340
You gave the red porcelain vase to her,

145
00:06:42,900 --> 00:06:43,900
instead of me.

146
00:06:44,700 --> 00:06:46,140
I had no choice,

147
00:06:46,140 --> 00:06:47,940
but to use a broken vase.

148
00:06:49,100 --> 00:06:51,140
Noble Consort Zhang has a red porcelain vase?

149
00:06:59,780 --> 00:07:00,660
You all know?

150
00:07:03,260 --> 00:07:04,500
I’m not sure

151
00:07:04,780 --> 00:07:05,780
if they all know.

152
00:07:06,300 --> 00:07:08,020
But I saw it by chance

153
00:07:08,420 --> 00:07:09,740
when the vase was taken into the palace.

154
00:07:10,780 --> 00:07:13,100
Her maids yelled loudly

155
00:07:13,220 --> 00:07:14,820
and cursed the senior eunuch on duty.

156
00:07:15,420 --> 00:07:17,300
“You can’t even find it in the palace.

157
00:07:17,820 --> 00:07:19,860
If you break something,

158
00:07:20,260 --> 00:07:21,780
you can’t pay the price even if you die.”

159
00:07:47,820 --> 00:07:49,260
= The Hall of Glory =
Madam asked you not to get in,

160
00:07:49,580 --> 00:07:50,740
because she didn’t want to see you.

161
00:07:51,540 --> 00:07:52,700
You should have waited

162
00:07:52,700 --> 00:07:53,580
at the door

163
00:07:53,820 --> 00:07:55,260
for her order.

164
00:07:56,020 --> 00:07:57,020
Did she not want you to get in

165
00:07:57,300 --> 00:07:58,460
because she wanted you to rest

166
00:07:58,700 --> 00:07:59,540
or wander about?

167
00:08:00,580 --> 00:08:01,700
What idiots!

168
00:08:04,980 --> 00:08:05,740
Your Majesty?

169
00:08:13,020 --> 00:08:14,580
Madam, His Majesty has arrived.

170
00:08:27,660 --> 00:08:29,500
Greetings, Your Majesty.

171
00:08:51,860 --> 00:08:52,820
You don’t like the dishes?

172
00:08:54,700 --> 00:08:55,460
Not really.

173
00:08:57,860 --> 00:08:59,340
Why don’t you have maids serve you?

174
00:09:02,860 --> 00:09:03,700
I used to

175
00:09:04,180 --> 00:09:05,940
have Aunt Jia serve me at dinner.

176
00:09:08,700 --> 00:09:10,020
Don’t go too far.

177
00:09:11,900 --> 00:09:13,180
What Jia Yulan did...

178
00:09:13,820 --> 00:09:14,900
If I wanted to punish her,

179
00:09:15,420 --> 00:09:17,020
I could have executed all her families.

180
00:09:19,180 --> 00:09:20,340
She doesn’t have any families

181
00:09:20,340 --> 00:09:21,420
for your execution.

182
00:09:21,860 --> 00:09:24,100
She’s an orphan, just like me.

183
00:09:24,820 --> 00:09:27,140
We have no one to depend on or care for.

184
00:09:43,420 --> 00:09:44,540
Where did you get the vase?

185
00:09:48,620 --> 00:09:49,660
From Mrs. Xue,

186
00:09:49,860 --> 00:09:50,980
Wang Gongchen’s wife.

187
00:09:52,820 --> 00:09:53,860
Do you know

188
00:09:55,020 --> 00:09:56,420
this is a red porcelain vase from Dingzhou?

189
00:10:00,660 --> 00:10:01,700
She told me so.

190
00:10:04,780 --> 00:10:06,500
Red porcelains are rare to be seen.

191
00:10:06,540 --> 00:10:07,500
It’s hard to produce them

192
00:10:07,780 --> 00:10:09,220
or control the colors.

193
00:10:09,220 --> 00:10:10,380
Every product is precious.

194
00:10:10,900 --> 00:10:12,020
I told you.

195
00:10:12,540 --> 00:10:14,340
No one in the palace shall use luxury goods.

196
00:10:14,940 --> 00:10:15,940
Years ago, I prohibited Dingzhou

197
00:10:15,940 --> 00:10:17,420
from paying red porcelains as tribute.

198
00:10:19,100 --> 00:10:20,020
Oh, you did?

199
00:10:22,380 --> 00:10:24,140
You’ve given me a lot of

200
00:10:24,580 --> 00:10:26,740
pearls, jades, and red corals.

201
00:10:27,940 --> 00:10:29,460
I didn’t know

202
00:10:30,180 --> 00:10:31,180
such jewels

203
00:10:31,780 --> 00:10:33,780
could be less precious than a mere vase.

204
00:10:38,180 --> 00:10:39,060
Besides,

205
00:10:39,740 --> 00:10:41,540
days ago, you just said

206
00:10:42,260 --> 00:10:43,660
you would give me anything

207
00:10:43,900 --> 00:10:45,260
as long as I didn’t hurt people

208
00:10:46,140 --> 00:10:48,020
or provoke Her Highness.

209
00:10:51,380 --> 00:10:52,540
Your father loves you.

210
00:10:53,580 --> 00:10:54,460
But you embarrassed him

211
00:10:54,460 --> 00:10:55,460
in front of

212
00:10:55,460 --> 00:10:56,460
so many madams.

213
00:10:57,420 --> 00:10:58,780
You used to be obedient.

214
00:10:59,380 --> 00:11:01,020
Why are you worse when you grow up?

215
00:11:02,020 --> 00:11:03,780
Madam Zhang embarrassed father,

216
00:11:04,060 --> 00:11:04,860
not me.

217
00:11:04,860 --> 00:11:05,620
Huirou.

218
00:11:06,060 --> 00:11:07,100
Father prohibited from paying red porcelains

219
00:11:07,100 --> 00:11:08,420
as tribute to him.

220
00:11:08,620 --> 00:11:10,220
After she was promoted,

221
00:11:10,340 --> 00:11:11,180
she accepted awards from officials

222
00:11:11,180 --> 00:11:12,420
in a flagrant way.

223
00:11:13,140 --> 00:11:14,780
She was promoted directly to Noble Consort.

224
00:11:15,260 --> 00:11:16,900
Such an unconventional promotion

225
00:11:17,300 --> 00:11:18,420
doesn’t show people

226
00:11:18,740 --> 00:11:20,100
her virtue or performance

227
00:11:20,100 --> 00:11:21,100
better than ordinary madams,

228
00:11:21,460 --> 00:11:22,780
but makes them

229
00:11:22,780 --> 00:11:23,660
violate father’s prohibition.

230
00:11:24,340 --> 00:11:25,100
Huirou.

231
00:11:26,180 --> 00:11:27,140
As daughter,

232
00:11:27,980 --> 00:11:28,940
you complain about your father.

233
00:11:29,740 --> 00:11:31,100
Who taught you that?

234
00:11:35,660 --> 00:11:37,500
Since I was little, I’ve been convinced

235
00:11:38,140 --> 00:11:39,260
by whatever you teach me.

236
00:11:39,860 --> 00:11:41,420
That’s because

237
00:11:41,780 --> 00:11:42,700
you’re a model for women

238
00:11:42,700 --> 00:11:43,860
in my heart.

239
00:11:44,460 --> 00:11:45,460
I didn’t dare to

240
00:11:45,460 --> 00:11:47,100
violate your instruction.

241
00:11:48,260 --> 00:11:49,500
But however hard I think about it,

242
00:11:49,780 --> 00:11:50,780
I can’t understand

243
00:11:51,860 --> 00:11:53,180
why you taught me

244
00:11:53,180 --> 00:11:54,340
in a way

245
00:11:55,260 --> 00:11:56,380
since I was little,

246
00:11:56,580 --> 00:11:58,380
but offered to promote Madam Zhang.

247
00:12:19,380 --> 00:12:20,180
So...

248
00:12:20,500 --> 00:12:21,940
That day, Mrs. Xue said

249
00:12:22,620 --> 00:12:23,780
she wanted to give me a gift

250
00:12:24,100 --> 00:12:25,620
for my promotion.

251
00:12:25,980 --> 00:12:28,020
She noticed there wasn’t anything eye-catching

252
00:12:28,580 --> 00:12:30,300
in my palace.

253
00:12:30,940 --> 00:12:31,780
Then,

254
00:12:32,260 --> 00:12:33,500
she said she would give me a rare vase

255
00:12:33,500 --> 00:12:35,380
that couldn’t be found in the palace.

256
00:12:36,220 --> 00:12:37,020
I thought,

257
00:12:37,940 --> 00:12:39,140
since you said

258
00:12:39,940 --> 00:12:40,860
I could ask for anything

259
00:12:41,140 --> 00:12:43,060
in this world,

260
00:12:44,060 --> 00:12:44,780
I would just accept

261
00:12:44,780 --> 00:12:46,580
a unique red vase

262
00:12:47,340 --> 00:12:48,300
if she insisted on

263
00:12:49,060 --> 00:12:50,220
giving it to me.

264
00:12:53,220 --> 00:12:54,580
Your Majesty, you’re going back on

265
00:12:55,460 --> 00:12:56,820
what you said?

266
00:13:00,660 --> 00:13:01,780
Fine,

267
00:13:02,220 --> 00:13:03,340
take the vase.

268
00:13:04,220 --> 00:13:05,940
Give it to whomever you like.

269
00:13:06,660 --> 00:13:08,140
I don’t care.

270
00:13:18,340 --> 00:13:19,700
I’m not going back on my words.

271
00:13:21,140 --> 00:13:22,100
I mean.

272
00:13:22,140 --> 00:13:23,500
Let me know if you want anything.

273
00:13:23,500 --> 00:13:24,820
I’ll try to get it to you.

274
00:13:25,740 --> 00:13:27,260
Who allowed you to contact officials

275
00:13:27,260 --> 00:13:28,300
and accept awards?

276
00:13:30,060 --> 00:13:31,300
I love you and care for you.

277
00:13:31,340 --> 00:13:32,580
But you threaten me with my love?

278
00:13:34,540 --> 00:13:36,180
When can you be mature?

279
00:13:38,260 --> 00:13:39,220
Love me? Care for me?

280
00:13:40,540 --> 00:13:41,260
All right.

281
00:13:42,380 --> 00:13:43,660
As long as you promise

282
00:13:43,740 --> 00:13:45,820
to investigate who framed up Aunt Jia

283
00:13:46,460 --> 00:13:48,060
and execute Zhang Maoze and his master

284
00:13:48,060 --> 00:13:49,940
who killed her with a plot...

285
00:13:50,660 --> 00:13:52,180
I am Zhang Maoze’s master!

286
00:14:03,940 --> 00:14:04,900
No madams can

287
00:14:05,300 --> 00:14:07,020
accept awards from officials.

288
00:14:07,740 --> 00:14:09,060
All of you, look carefully.

289
00:14:09,460 --> 00:14:10,740
I smashed the vase.

290
00:14:11,140 --> 00:14:12,540
If anyone of you dares to incite her

291
00:14:12,540 --> 00:14:13,740
to accept awards from officials,

292
00:14:13,860 --> 00:14:15,420
I’ll behead you!

293
00:14:31,540 --> 00:14:33,020
Your Highness, I also want to ask you.

294
00:14:33,620 --> 00:14:34,660
Do imperial rules

295
00:14:34,860 --> 00:14:36,060
vary from person to person?

296
00:14:36,940 --> 00:14:38,100
Huirou, shut up!

297
00:14:38,540 --> 00:14:40,020
Go back to your room and kneel.

298
00:14:41,900 --> 00:14:42,620
Your Highness.

299
00:14:42,620 --> 00:14:43,820
I’ve spoilt her.

300
00:14:44,340 --> 00:14:45,180
Dinner time

301
00:14:45,180 --> 00:14:46,340
is over.

302
00:14:46,460 --> 00:14:47,140
Shall we...

303
00:14:48,620 --> 00:14:49,380
Huirou.

304
00:15:09,540 --> 00:15:10,900
You’ve grown up.

305
00:15:12,820 --> 00:15:14,380
I should no longer treat you

306
00:15:14,380 --> 00:15:15,220
as a little girl.

307
00:15:19,420 --> 00:15:22,020
All right. Let me tell you

308
00:15:22,540 --> 00:15:24,620
why I promoted Madam Zhang.

309
00:15:29,620 --> 00:15:30,700
Because I...

310
00:15:30,940 --> 00:15:32,700
I want to make your father happier

311
00:15:33,260 --> 00:15:34,500
and less upset.

312
00:15:36,220 --> 00:15:37,820
Are you scared of father?

313
00:15:42,340 --> 00:15:43,460
I love him.

314
00:15:45,380 --> 00:15:46,820
Then aren’t you angry?

315
00:15:47,460 --> 00:15:48,740
I love father.

316
00:15:49,540 --> 00:15:50,940
That’s why

317
00:15:51,140 --> 00:15:52,340
I’m so angry

318
00:15:52,660 --> 00:15:53,700
for his unfairness.

319
00:15:54,460 --> 00:15:57,540
Father asked me to

320
00:15:58,100 --> 00:15:59,500
learn from you and mother

321
00:15:59,540 --> 00:16:00,900
to be a gentle and kind girl.

322
00:16:01,620 --> 00:16:03,300
But he allows Madam Zhang

323
00:16:03,540 --> 00:16:05,540
to be arrogant and greedy

324
00:16:05,740 --> 00:16:07,300
and even made her Noble Consort.

325
00:16:15,460 --> 00:16:16,300
Huirou.

326
00:16:17,980 --> 00:16:19,180
You’ve grown up.

327
00:16:20,100 --> 00:16:21,140
Gradually, you will know

328
00:16:22,060 --> 00:16:24,140
most things are unsatisfactory.

329
00:16:27,500 --> 00:16:29,260
It took me a very long time

330
00:16:29,460 --> 00:16:30,380
to figure it out.

331
00:16:31,420 --> 00:16:33,820
We can live a more comfortable life

332
00:16:34,460 --> 00:16:36,380
when we tolerate

333
00:16:36,500 --> 00:16:37,660
something or someone we don’t like

334
00:16:38,420 --> 00:16:39,700
for something or someone we like.

335
00:16:42,420 --> 00:16:43,940
You say you love father.

336
00:16:45,780 --> 00:16:47,660
You love him and you must forbear yourself

337
00:16:49,020 --> 00:16:50,020
and tolerate others.

338
00:16:53,260 --> 00:16:54,180
Then I hope

339
00:16:54,700 --> 00:16:55,580
I won’t ever love someone

340
00:16:55,580 --> 00:16:56,460
like this!

341
00:16:58,460 --> 00:16:59,220
Huirou.

342
00:17:02,060 --> 00:17:03,500
Don’t be angry with her, Your Highness.

343
00:17:05,500 --> 00:17:06,780
I won’t.

344
00:17:16,020 --> 00:17:17,020
But she is

345
00:17:18,260 --> 00:17:19,340
too fiery.

346
00:17:23,820 --> 00:17:24,940
Now I feel

347
00:17:25,700 --> 00:17:27,260
it’s her luck when His Majesty

348
00:17:27,260 --> 00:17:28,620
doesn’t marry her to my nephew.

349
00:17:30,660 --> 00:17:31,660
He is a romantic man.

350
00:17:32,940 --> 00:17:34,740
Huirou can’t tolerate that.

351
00:17:37,740 --> 00:17:39,020
But she...

352
00:17:39,780 --> 00:17:40,900
she’s too stubborn.

353
00:17:42,140 --> 00:17:43,900
She doesn’t like her future husband.

354
00:17:46,180 --> 00:17:47,860
I don’t know what a life she’ll live

355
00:17:49,460 --> 00:17:50,940
after she gets married.

356
00:18:23,740 --> 00:18:24,500
Your Majesty.

357
00:18:28,460 --> 00:18:29,500
There you are, Your Majesty.

358
00:18:31,500 --> 00:18:32,260
Be seated.

359
00:18:56,260 --> 00:18:57,580
You must be coming for Huirou,

360
00:18:58,260 --> 00:18:59,500
aren’t you?

361
00:19:01,500 --> 00:19:03,460
Your Majesty, don’t be angry with her.

362
00:19:04,260 --> 00:19:06,100
She loves you too much.

363
00:19:06,500 --> 00:19:07,500
And she’s jealous.

364
00:19:08,660 --> 00:19:10,820
She’s a reasonable girl.

365
00:19:11,260 --> 00:19:13,780
She’ll be convinced soon.

366
00:19:18,180 --> 00:19:19,220
In fact,

367
00:19:21,300 --> 00:19:22,860
I also want you

368
00:19:24,300 --> 00:19:25,740
to persuade Madam Zhang.

369
00:19:27,900 --> 00:19:28,820
First,

370
00:19:29,500 --> 00:19:32,100
ask her to restrain her chief maid.

371
00:19:32,660 --> 00:19:33,420
Second...

372
00:19:33,420 --> 00:19:34,300
Bihan is always wayward.

373
00:19:36,180 --> 00:19:37,620
She has made a lot of trouble to you.

374
00:19:40,860 --> 00:19:41,620
I...

375
00:19:44,980 --> 00:19:46,340
I don’t have the heart to punish her.

376
00:19:48,900 --> 00:19:50,620
She gave birth to three daughters,

377
00:19:51,740 --> 00:19:54,020
but all of them passed away.

378
00:19:55,460 --> 00:19:56,820
Whenever I’m angry with her,

379
00:19:58,100 --> 00:19:58,940
I remember that

380
00:19:58,940 --> 00:20:00,340
she held Youwu in her arms.

381
00:20:00,740 --> 00:20:01,780
She said

382
00:20:02,900 --> 00:20:04,460
she would want nothing else,

383
00:20:05,460 --> 00:20:06,620
except the health of our daughter.

384
00:20:12,740 --> 00:20:14,500
I know it’s difficult for you, Your Majesty.

385
00:20:15,460 --> 00:20:16,220
So,

386
00:20:16,300 --> 00:20:18,020
I offered to promote her

387
00:20:18,220 --> 00:20:19,700
with my true heart.

388
00:20:22,260 --> 00:20:25,820
I wanted to make you feel better.

389
00:20:29,820 --> 00:20:30,620
Danshu.

390
00:20:32,060 --> 00:20:32,860
I...

391
00:20:35,300 --> 00:20:36,700
I owe you too much.

392
00:20:44,140 --> 00:20:45,020
When you were young,

393
00:20:45,020 --> 00:20:46,420
you refused to learn embroidery carefully.

394
00:20:46,620 --> 00:20:49,180
Why do you work so hard now?

395
00:20:51,980 --> 00:20:53,220
I was wayward when I was little.

396
00:20:54,180 --> 00:20:55,300
And I have many elder brothers.

397
00:20:55,980 --> 00:20:57,220
On the day I was born,

398
00:20:57,420 --> 00:20:58,660
my uncle turned the tables

399
00:20:58,700 --> 00:20:59,780
and won a big victory.

400
00:21:00,380 --> 00:21:01,260
They thought

401
00:21:01,260 --> 00:21:02,620
I brought the luck.

402
00:21:03,580 --> 00:21:04,740
Many elder members in my family

403
00:21:04,820 --> 00:21:06,060
spoilt me a lot.

404
00:21:07,460 --> 00:21:09,260
No wonder you dared to defend Fan Zhongyan

405
00:21:09,260 --> 00:21:10,980
in Nanjing.

406
00:21:12,060 --> 00:21:13,100
Why are you bringing up

407
00:21:13,100 --> 00:21:14,340
the old story again?

408
00:21:17,620 --> 00:21:18,660
Thinking of that,

409
00:21:19,660 --> 00:21:20,980
I was just like a playboy

410
00:21:21,620 --> 00:21:23,220
at that time.

411
00:21:24,980 --> 00:21:25,900
Your Majesty.

412
00:21:26,700 --> 00:21:28,140
Are you going to mock me with this

413
00:21:28,860 --> 00:21:30,340
all my life?

414
00:21:31,620 --> 00:21:32,820
Then tell me more interesting stories

415
00:21:32,820 --> 00:21:33,860
in your childhood

416
00:21:34,540 --> 00:21:35,460
so that I can mock you

417
00:21:35,460 --> 00:21:36,980
with more examples.

418
00:21:41,620 --> 00:21:42,300
What do you mean?

419
00:21:48,100 --> 00:21:49,220
I want to know more,

420
00:21:49,740 --> 00:21:50,820
when you were younger,

421
00:21:51,740 --> 00:21:53,900
when you played martial arts with your brothers,

422
00:21:54,460 --> 00:21:56,380
when you studied better than them

423
00:21:56,380 --> 00:21:57,300
and you were proud,

424
00:21:57,820 --> 00:21:59,580
when you knew your future husband

425
00:21:59,620 --> 00:22:00,740
only wanted immortal cultivation,

426
00:22:01,180 --> 00:22:02,540
but you kept your promise

427
00:22:02,900 --> 00:22:04,580
and put on the wedding dress.

428
00:22:08,580 --> 00:22:09,780
At that time,

429
00:22:12,020 --> 00:22:13,100
I wasn’t scared of anything.

430
00:22:15,300 --> 00:22:16,500
When I first married,

431
00:22:17,260 --> 00:22:18,980
the husband my grandpa picked for me

432
00:22:19,620 --> 00:22:20,540
wanted only immortal cultivation.

433
00:22:21,860 --> 00:22:22,740
On the wedding night,

434
00:22:23,580 --> 00:22:24,980
he stared at me

435
00:22:25,500 --> 00:22:26,700
as if I were a monster.

436
00:22:29,420 --> 00:22:30,540
I told him,

437
00:22:31,540 --> 00:22:32,340
“Don’t be scared.

438
00:22:32,780 --> 00:22:34,180
I won’t force you.”

439
00:22:35,140 --> 00:22:37,980
Meanwhile, I wrote the letter of divorce.

440
00:22:39,060 --> 00:22:40,540
Didn’t you feel sad at all?

441
00:22:42,700 --> 00:22:44,540
I just remembered

442
00:22:46,060 --> 00:22:48,020
I kept talking to myself that

443
00:22:49,340 --> 00:22:50,460
it wasn’t my bad.

444
00:22:52,460 --> 00:22:53,260
I just had bad luck.

445
00:22:54,020 --> 00:22:54,940
I wasn’t scared.

446
00:22:55,900 --> 00:22:58,460
I was able to live a good life.

447
00:22:59,100 --> 00:23:00,180
I wouldn’t let myself

448
00:23:00,180 --> 00:23:01,820
live a poor life.

449
00:23:08,580 --> 00:23:11,940
I think it was my silliness and arrogance

450
00:23:13,140 --> 00:23:14,300
that annoyed the heaven.

451
00:23:16,020 --> 00:23:17,580
Then I was an ugly monster in the newspaper

452
00:23:18,100 --> 00:23:20,140
who scared away her husband.

453
00:23:21,100 --> 00:23:22,180
Youheng and Qingsu

454
00:23:22,260 --> 00:23:23,340
took up the cudgel for me.

455
00:23:24,260 --> 00:23:25,380
But I joked with that.

456
00:23:26,940 --> 00:23:28,580
Later, I was chosen to be your wife.

457
00:23:28,990 --> 00:23:32,350
♪ Loved you a gentleman ♪

458
00:23:32,380 --> 00:23:33,180
That day...

459
00:23:34,410 --> 00:23:38,500
♪ Yet got abandoned ♪

460
00:23:40,010 --> 00:23:42,880
♪ Peach blossoms ♪

461
00:23:43,860 --> 00:23:44,700
Danshu.

462
00:23:44,700 --> 00:23:47,340
♪ Color the city ♪

463
00:23:47,460 --> 00:23:48,460
When I grew up,

464
00:23:50,580 --> 00:23:51,860
I met more unsatisfactory things.

465
00:23:52,580 --> 00:23:54,020
I was no longer arrogant.

466
00:23:57,380 --> 00:23:58,460
I’m the one

467
00:24:00,260 --> 00:24:01,780
who has done most unsatisfactory things to you.

468
00:24:03,860 --> 00:24:04,980
Am I right?

469
00:24:04,980 --> 00:24:09,130
♪ Bid farewell with wine after the glory ends ♪

470
00:24:09,180 --> 00:24:09,980
Your Majesty.

471
00:24:09,980 --> 00:24:13,820
♪ Outside the city a beautiful world unveils ♪

472
00:24:13,860 --> 00:24:15,020
On the wedding night,

473
00:24:17,380 --> 00:24:18,220
I was...

474
00:24:18,260 --> 00:24:22,070
♪ Long-standing distance doesn’t alienate us ♪

475
00:24:22,070 --> 00:24:23,940
♪ Keep you company behind the gate ♪

476
00:24:24,020 --> 00:24:25,580
I didn’t have a choice,

477
00:24:26,100 --> 00:24:27,820
but to make you the Empress.

478
00:24:29,700 --> 00:24:31,780
I thought I was aggrieved.

479
00:24:31,780 --> 00:24:32,820
I didn’t know

480
00:24:33,580 --> 00:24:34,660
you were even more aggrieved.

481
00:24:38,060 --> 00:24:40,740
Even though you were aggrieved,

482
00:24:40,740 --> 00:24:42,220
you tried your best to be a good empress.

483
00:24:43,060 --> 00:24:44,460
Yet I didn’t cherish you.

484
00:24:45,820 --> 00:24:47,380
I locked such a brave and bright girl

485
00:24:48,620 --> 00:24:50,860
like you in the palace.

486
00:24:52,060 --> 00:24:53,940
And I treated you coldly over the decade,

487
00:24:56,060 --> 00:24:57,260
making you sad for half of your life.

488
00:24:57,260 --> 00:25:00,950
♪ Hold your hands and go home together ♪

489
00:25:07,260 --> 00:25:08,020
Your Majesty.

490
00:25:09,260 --> 00:25:10,420
You don’t feel well?

491
00:25:14,500 --> 00:25:16,820
It’s okay. I have the medicine with me.

492
00:25:17,340 --> 00:25:18,420
Don’t disturb others.

493
00:25:19,260 --> 00:25:21,060
Don’t let Huirou know or she’ll worry.

494
00:25:23,100 --> 00:25:23,860
Okay.

495
00:25:32,260 --> 00:25:34,740
They’re in the wrong.

496
00:25:35,420 --> 00:25:37,060
It’s understandable

497
00:25:37,340 --> 00:25:38,580
if we detain Yelv Hongji.

498
00:25:40,020 --> 00:25:41,100
I think...

499
00:25:41,940 --> 00:25:43,380
I admire you, Your Majesty.

500
00:25:44,820 --> 00:25:45,940
So, I try my best

501
00:25:47,020 --> 00:25:48,660
to see how you behave

502
00:25:49,540 --> 00:25:51,980
and guess what you think of.

503
00:25:53,580 --> 00:25:55,100
To learn to be a leader,

504
00:25:56,300 --> 00:25:57,860
you’re my best example.

505
00:25:59,140 --> 00:26:01,260
Yelv Hongji has sneaked into our territory.

506
00:26:01,380 --> 00:26:03,500
It’s hard to know what he wants.

507
00:26:04,300 --> 00:26:06,820
But I don’t think

508
00:26:07,260 --> 00:26:08,540
he comes here

509
00:26:08,620 --> 00:26:10,740
because he admires us.

510
00:26:14,420 --> 00:26:15,460
Admire!

511
00:26:18,060 --> 00:26:19,380
That’s right.

512
00:26:20,940 --> 00:26:21,620
Uh...

513
00:26:25,010 --> 00:26:26,810
You’re honest and diligent.

514
00:26:27,010 --> 00:26:29,050
You often give me good advice.

515
00:26:29,650 --> 00:26:31,370
= He Tan, courtesy name Shengcong =
You’re a loyal official.

516
00:26:31,890 --> 00:26:34,330
I didn’t want you to leave the Capital.

517
00:26:34,610 --> 00:26:36,410
But you ask to

518
00:26:36,410 --> 00:26:37,770
work in your hometown

519
00:26:37,890 --> 00:26:39,210
so that you can accompany your old mother.

520
00:26:39,770 --> 00:26:40,970
I can decline anything,

521
00:26:41,290 --> 00:26:43,450
expect your filial piety to your mother.

522
00:26:47,770 --> 00:26:49,810
Thank you for understanding, Your Majesty.

523
00:26:57,530 --> 00:26:58,570
I always want to tell you something,

524
00:27:00,090 --> 00:27:02,290
but I haven’t.

525
00:27:04,330 --> 00:27:06,530
Since I’m leaving the Capital,

526
00:27:07,050 --> 00:27:08,970
I must tell you before that.

527
00:27:09,330 --> 00:27:11,530
Or I’m too ashamed to be an official.

528
00:27:13,410 --> 00:27:14,410
Go ahead.

529
00:27:15,890 --> 00:27:16,570
I don’t think

530
00:27:18,170 --> 00:27:19,770
Noble Consort Zhang’s uncle Zhang Yaozuo

531
00:27:19,770 --> 00:27:22,090
should be the Supervisor of Finance.

532
00:27:23,290 --> 00:27:24,330
I should have told you earlier.

533
00:27:24,970 --> 00:27:26,050
But I know

534
00:27:26,130 --> 00:27:27,890
you always spoil Noble Consort Zhang.

535
00:27:29,130 --> 00:27:30,410
In case of hurting you,

536
00:27:30,970 --> 00:27:31,930
I hesitated for long.

537
00:27:32,890 --> 00:27:35,770
Today, you said I was a loyal official.

538
00:27:37,330 --> 00:27:38,530
But I feel ashamed.

539
00:27:45,930 --> 00:27:47,610
Zhang Yaozuo was a scholar.

540
00:27:48,410 --> 00:27:50,290
He isn’t a bad guy.

541
00:27:50,970 --> 00:27:52,210
Since he was the Supervisor of Finance,

542
00:27:52,730 --> 00:27:53,810
he hasn’t grabbed all the power.

543
00:27:54,290 --> 00:27:56,130
I don’t think you need to accuse him.

544
00:27:58,130 --> 00:27:59,370
Speaking of talent,

545
00:27:59,690 --> 00:28:01,170
Zhang Yaozuo was a scholar.

546
00:28:01,450 --> 00:28:02,650
He isn’t a bad guy.

547
00:28:03,330 --> 00:28:04,690
But for the sake of our nation,

548
00:28:05,250 --> 00:28:08,010
Supervisor of Finance shouldn’t be a relative.

549
00:28:08,690 --> 00:28:09,690
Considering your reputation,

550
00:28:10,050 --> 00:28:12,650
You shouldn’t promote a madam’s relative

551
00:28:13,090 --> 00:28:14,890
only because you love her.

552
00:28:15,930 --> 00:28:18,010
The Supervisor of Finance

553
00:28:18,130 --> 00:28:19,410
will easily be promoted to minister.

554
00:28:19,730 --> 00:28:21,330
Zhang Yaozuo is already the Supervisor of Finance.

555
00:28:21,810 --> 00:28:22,570
After the sacrificial rites,

556
00:28:22,810 --> 00:28:24,210
someone will certainly advise you

557
00:28:24,490 --> 00:28:26,250
to promote him into the Cabinet or Privy Council.

558
00:28:26,690 --> 00:28:27,410
By then,

559
00:28:27,610 --> 00:28:29,690
censors will try desperately

560
00:28:29,690 --> 00:28:30,530
to stop Zhang Yaozuo from being promoted.

561
00:28:31,010 --> 00:28:32,330
They’ll even risk their lives.

562
00:28:32,370 --> 00:28:33,650
When they’re quarreling,

563
00:28:33,930 --> 00:28:36,090
what decision will you make?

564
00:28:37,930 --> 00:28:39,490
If you use Yaozuo

565
00:28:39,530 --> 00:28:41,090
and demote censors,

566
00:28:41,610 --> 00:28:43,530
your reputation will be ruined.

567
00:28:43,810 --> 00:28:48,010
If you fire Yaozuo because of censors,

568
00:28:49,370 --> 00:28:52,290
Noble Consort Zhang will blame you.

569
00:28:55,290 --> 00:28:56,370
Chuyue was gone.

570
00:28:57,690 --> 00:28:58,930
Yaoyao passed away.

571
00:29:00,570 --> 00:29:02,010
So did Youwu.

572
00:29:03,490 --> 00:29:05,850
Even Aunt Jia left me.

573
00:29:16,900 --> 00:29:18,540
Too much favor for a madam’s relative

574
00:29:18,580 --> 00:29:19,660
will bring trouble.

575
00:29:20,380 --> 00:29:21,500
It’s safe

576
00:29:21,740 --> 00:29:22,660
when you control what he can get.

577
00:29:23,100 --> 00:29:24,180
I’ve thought carefully about it.

578
00:29:24,620 --> 00:29:25,740
Your uncle Li Yonghe

579
00:29:25,740 --> 00:29:26,900
is a good example.

580
00:29:27,220 --> 00:29:29,900
You can also give Zhang Yaozuo great wealth

581
00:29:30,180 --> 00:29:31,100
instead of real power.

582
00:29:32,580 --> 00:29:34,820
I’m considering for your reputation.

583
00:29:35,620 --> 00:29:36,540
Your reputation

584
00:29:36,540 --> 00:29:37,900
is the best confidence

585
00:29:37,900 --> 00:29:40,020
that people have in the imperial court.

586
00:29:41,180 --> 00:29:41,940
Your Majesty!

587
00:29:48,540 --> 00:29:49,460
Go to the storehouse

588
00:29:49,580 --> 00:29:50,940
and look for two best vases.

589
00:29:51,180 --> 00:29:51,980
Send one

590
00:29:52,820 --> 00:29:54,220
to Pavilion of Phoenix by yourself.

591
00:29:54,220 --> 00:29:55,100
Tell Huirou

592
00:29:55,260 --> 00:29:56,340
it’s my gift for her.

593
00:29:58,260 --> 00:29:59,140
Have the other one

594
00:30:00,700 --> 00:30:01,820
sent to the Hall of Glory.

595
00:30:03,220 --> 00:30:04,500
Madam, you know.

596
00:30:04,900 --> 00:30:06,580
Your uncle and cousin

597
00:30:06,980 --> 00:30:08,020
passed the imperial exams

598
00:30:08,220 --> 00:30:09,700
and became scholars.

599
00:30:10,220 --> 00:30:12,340
They have real capabilities.

600
00:30:13,220 --> 00:30:14,380
Your uncle is

601
00:30:14,460 --> 00:30:15,900
cautious in working.

602
00:30:16,940 --> 00:30:18,860
He never bullies people with his power.

603
00:30:18,940 --> 00:30:20,900
Nor does he accumulate wealth.

604
00:30:21,260 --> 00:30:22,620
But those meddlesome censors

605
00:30:22,620 --> 00:30:24,300
= Zhang Yaozuo’s Wife =
still keep an eye on him,

606
00:30:24,660 --> 00:30:27,860
as if he took too much advantage of you.

607
00:30:29,140 --> 00:30:30,700
Before I served His Majesty,

608
00:30:30,820 --> 00:30:32,420
Uncle had passed the imperial exam.

609
00:30:32,940 --> 00:30:34,460
He wasn’t promoted in years.

610
00:30:35,780 --> 00:30:37,460
He was an official of low rank

611
00:30:38,220 --> 00:30:39,460
in 1041 A.D.,

612
00:30:39,500 --> 00:30:40,740
and soon became Supervisor of Finance

613
00:30:41,140 --> 00:30:43,220
after I won His Majesty’s love.

614
00:30:43,740 --> 00:30:45,460
Was it because of his own capacity?

615
00:30:47,500 --> 00:30:49,380
Did I

616
00:30:50,060 --> 00:30:51,700
help him with his career

617
00:30:52,020 --> 00:30:53,740
or make trouble for him?

618
00:30:54,820 --> 00:30:56,220
You certainly

619
00:30:56,220 --> 00:30:58,220
bring honor to the Zhangs.

620
00:30:59,060 --> 00:31:01,340
Raising a daughter like you

621
00:31:01,500 --> 00:31:02,820
is better than raising ten sons like scholars.

622
00:31:04,300 --> 00:31:05,260
I hear

623
00:31:05,740 --> 00:31:08,340
you’ve been angry with His Majesty.

624
00:31:08,820 --> 00:31:12,100
For Aunt Jia?

625
00:31:13,860 --> 00:31:14,940
It was the plot of

626
00:31:16,860 --> 00:31:18,620
the so-called empress.

627
00:31:19,500 --> 00:31:21,700
His Majesty was deceived by her, too.

628
00:31:23,140 --> 00:31:23,900
But...

629
00:31:24,580 --> 00:31:26,140
Your uncle and I thought it over.

630
00:31:26,820 --> 00:31:29,340
You shouldn’t be angry with the wrong person.

631
00:31:30,180 --> 00:31:31,820
If you’re angry with His Majesty,

632
00:31:32,260 --> 00:31:33,180
you won’t feel close to him.

633
00:31:33,540 --> 00:31:34,460
Then you’ll fall into

634
00:31:34,620 --> 00:31:36,740
the Empress’s trap.

635
00:31:38,660 --> 00:31:39,580
Madam.

636
00:31:40,260 --> 00:31:41,340
You live in the palace,

637
00:31:41,500 --> 00:31:42,700
all by yourself.

638
00:31:43,580 --> 00:31:46,300
His Majesty is the only one to rely on.

639
00:31:47,300 --> 00:31:48,700
If you want to avenge Aunt Jia,

640
00:31:49,660 --> 00:31:52,060
you shouldn’t act on impulse.

641
00:32:02,260 --> 00:32:03,140
Madam.

642
00:32:03,340 --> 00:32:04,860
Here’s a gift from His Majesty.

643
00:32:08,890 --> 00:32:11,130
She’s learning harp carefully.

644
00:32:12,060 --> 00:32:13,900
She practices it two or three hours every day.

645
00:32:14,940 --> 00:32:17,260
She even practices her fingers in bed.

646
00:32:18,500 --> 00:32:19,340
Lusi.

647
00:32:19,340 --> 00:32:20,780
Go get Huirou for lunch.

648
00:32:20,780 --> 00:32:21,620
Madam.

649
00:32:29,180 --> 00:32:29,940
Madam.

650
00:32:29,940 --> 00:32:31,220
Princess said

651
00:32:31,220 --> 00:32:32,740
she was enlightened today

652
00:32:32,980 --> 00:32:33,900
and wanted to practice for long,

653
00:32:33,900 --> 00:32:35,060
so that she would learn more.

654
00:32:35,180 --> 00:32:36,700
She just had some snacks.

655
00:32:36,780 --> 00:32:37,740
She isn’t coming for lunch.

656
00:32:40,340 --> 00:32:41,900
What’s wrong with her?

657
00:32:42,180 --> 00:32:43,500
She even doesn’t have lunch.

658
00:32:45,620 --> 00:32:47,140
His Majesty really loves you.

659
00:32:47,700 --> 00:32:50,540
Isn’t it a treasure from the Tang Dynasty?

660
00:32:51,220 --> 00:32:52,140
You can’t tell.

661
00:32:54,820 --> 00:32:55,900
I can’t.

662
00:32:56,300 --> 00:32:56,940
But...

663
00:32:57,180 --> 00:32:58,820
it’s a gift from His Majesty.

664
00:32:59,460 --> 00:33:00,540
His gift

665
00:33:01,340 --> 00:33:02,780
is smashing something

666
00:33:03,220 --> 00:33:04,500
and then giving something.

667
00:33:04,900 --> 00:33:05,860
Madam, you...

668
00:33:07,220 --> 00:33:09,620
All right. Shut up.

669
00:33:10,540 --> 00:33:12,300
I know in recent days

670
00:33:12,740 --> 00:33:14,380
many censors

671
00:33:14,380 --> 00:33:15,900
don’t want uncle to be Supervisor of Finance

672
00:33:16,420 --> 00:33:17,820
and they’re thinking how to impeach him.

673
00:33:19,660 --> 00:33:20,300
Madam.

674
00:33:20,500 --> 00:33:22,060
You must tell His Majesty.

675
00:33:22,340 --> 00:33:23,980
Your uncle has been

676
00:33:23,980 --> 00:33:24,860
diligent and assiduous.

677
00:33:25,140 --> 00:33:26,460
He wants to work for the imperial court.

678
00:33:27,580 --> 00:33:28,580
And he swears to

679
00:33:28,740 --> 00:33:29,780
win credit for you.

680
00:33:32,020 --> 00:33:32,860
Well,

681
00:33:33,420 --> 00:33:35,740
it’s okay to give up on that job.

682
00:33:37,540 --> 00:33:38,380
Madam.

683
00:33:38,700 --> 00:33:39,980
You can’t give in like that.

684
00:33:40,220 --> 00:33:42,900
Or the censors will be more arrogant.

685
00:33:44,420 --> 00:33:46,300
Mrs. Xue told me

686
00:33:47,060 --> 00:33:48,420
uncle couldn’t help me much

687
00:33:48,660 --> 00:33:49,940
when he was the Supervisor of Finance.

688
00:33:50,820 --> 00:33:51,820
As the Supervisor of Finance,

689
00:33:52,180 --> 00:33:53,420
whatever he does concerns the nation.

690
00:33:53,980 --> 00:33:55,620
Officials keep a close eye on him.

691
00:33:56,460 --> 00:33:57,580
Taking that job,

692
00:33:58,340 --> 00:33:59,140
he’s just a sitting duck

693
00:33:59,140 --> 00:34:00,140
and a target.

694
00:34:01,060 --> 00:34:02,140
It’s better to do a job

695
00:34:02,660 --> 00:34:04,140
where he can help me more.

696
00:34:04,940 --> 00:34:05,740
Uh... Uh...

697
00:34:06,220 --> 00:34:07,380
Wang Gongchen

698
00:34:07,380 --> 00:34:08,580
used to be a fence-sitter.

699
00:34:09,020 --> 00:34:09,820
Madam.

700
00:34:10,140 --> 00:34:11,620
Don’t trust him.

701
00:34:12,260 --> 00:34:13,860
He wanted to trap Ouyang Xiu

702
00:34:13,860 --> 00:34:15,460
for taking revenge.

703
00:34:15,740 --> 00:34:16,580
But he was also lofty

704
00:34:16,620 --> 00:34:18,140
and annoyed Xia Song’s subordinates.

705
00:34:18,340 --> 00:34:19,900
He has pleased no one.

706
00:34:19,900 --> 00:34:21,420
And they all hate him.

707
00:34:22,060 --> 00:34:23,340
Wang Gongchen and his wife

708
00:34:24,060 --> 00:34:25,140
treat me in a better way

709
00:34:25,140 --> 00:34:26,100
than you or uncle.

710
00:34:27,300 --> 00:34:28,140
I think

711
00:34:28,660 --> 00:34:30,340
Wang Gongchen and his wife are humane.

712
00:34:31,020 --> 00:34:32,500
They won’t kick out their poor families

713
00:34:32,500 --> 00:34:34,500
who ask for help.

714
00:34:37,540 --> 00:34:38,380
Anyway,

715
00:34:38,940 --> 00:34:40,580
I’m advising you for your own good.

716
00:34:40,940 --> 00:34:42,620
When you’re doing good, so are we.

717
00:34:43,020 --> 00:34:45,420
Then we can bring honor to you

718
00:34:45,660 --> 00:34:46,900
and work better for you.

719
00:34:48,020 --> 00:34:49,020
You’re telling me?

720
00:34:50,620 --> 00:34:51,820
If you couldn’t help me,

721
00:34:52,580 --> 00:34:53,620
why would I let such an idiot like you

722
00:34:53,620 --> 00:34:55,100
come to my chamber

723
00:34:55,100 --> 00:34:55,860
when you used to bully my mother?

724
00:34:56,500 --> 00:34:57,980
Do you think I want to see you?

725
00:35:04,860 --> 00:35:05,660
Get out.

726
00:35:39,820 --> 00:35:40,700
Aunt Li.

727
00:35:44,340 --> 00:35:44,980
Madam.

728
00:35:46,540 --> 00:35:48,100
Go and figure out

729
00:35:49,100 --> 00:35:50,020
if His Majesty gave me

730
00:35:50,660 --> 00:35:52,020
the vase alone,

731
00:35:52,260 --> 00:35:53,420
or if he gave it to someone else, too.

732
00:35:54,510 --> 00:35:55,180
Aye.

733
00:35:57,100 --> 00:35:57,980
Huaiji.

734
00:35:59,180 --> 00:36:01,180
Father asked you to give me the vase.

735
00:36:01,660 --> 00:36:03,340
Did he say anything?

736
00:36:05,380 --> 00:36:06,020
No.

737
00:36:06,660 --> 00:36:08,020
His Majesty asked me

738
00:36:08,020 --> 00:36:09,220
to pick the best vase in the storehouse.

739
00:36:12,140 --> 00:36:12,940
I suppose

740
00:36:13,220 --> 00:36:14,940
father thinks I gave a piece of good advice.

741
00:36:15,500 --> 00:36:16,820
He accepted my advice,

742
00:36:17,700 --> 00:36:18,860
but was too shy to praise me.

743
00:36:19,740 --> 00:36:21,260
So, he smashed the read porcelain vase

744
00:36:21,260 --> 00:36:22,540
Noble Consort Zhang accepted as bribe.

745
00:36:23,220 --> 00:36:25,140
Then he gave me a celadon vase.

746
00:36:30,620 --> 00:36:31,660
But Huaiji,

747
00:36:31,900 --> 00:36:33,540
I don’t care about any vase.

748
00:36:33,780 --> 00:36:34,740
I just want to ask father to let you

749
00:36:34,740 --> 00:36:36,020
stay with me for two hours a day.

750
00:36:39,020 --> 00:36:40,140
When I practice harp,

751
00:36:40,300 --> 00:36:41,340
you can learn the flute.

752
00:36:43,540 --> 00:36:44,780
You’re so smart.

753
00:36:44,900 --> 00:36:46,380
You’ll learn it faster than me.

754
00:36:47,500 --> 00:36:48,620
Go learn the flute,

755
00:36:48,780 --> 00:36:49,900
tune for me,

756
00:36:50,140 --> 00:36:51,140
and check my performance.

757
00:36:51,940 --> 00:36:53,100
Stay with me when I play the harp.

758
00:36:54,220 --> 00:36:54,940
Later,

759
00:36:55,900 --> 00:36:57,180
we can also perform together.

760
00:37:04,420 --> 00:37:06,300
His Majesty gave the vases to no one else,

761
00:37:06,660 --> 00:37:08,300
except you and Princess Fukang.

762
00:37:10,780 --> 00:37:11,580
Princess?

763
00:37:18,780 --> 00:37:20,420
What a drama queen!

764
00:37:20,940 --> 00:37:23,020
She is exactly instructed by the Empress.

765
00:37:24,860 --> 00:37:25,580
Madam.

766
00:37:26,180 --> 00:37:27,260
Princess Fukang

767
00:37:27,260 --> 00:37:28,660
is the only alive child of His Majesty.

768
00:37:29,060 --> 00:37:30,380
His Majesty spoils her for sure.

769
00:37:31,740 --> 00:37:33,260
She wanted all the other children to die,

770
00:37:34,140 --> 00:37:35,300
even including

771
00:37:35,300 --> 00:37:36,180
her own little brother.

772
00:37:36,420 --> 00:37:38,100
Sure, she’s the only child now

773
00:37:38,980 --> 00:37:40,100
and finds favor with her father.

774
00:37:42,700 --> 00:37:44,540
Aunt Li, tell me.

775
00:37:46,140 --> 00:37:47,540
Commissioner of Palace Attendants

776
00:37:48,260 --> 00:37:49,660
doesn’t sound

777
00:37:49,860 --> 00:37:50,780
as powerful as Supervisor of Finance.

778
00:37:51,820 --> 00:37:53,340
But a Commissioner takes charge of

779
00:37:53,460 --> 00:37:54,980
all bureaus in the imperial harems.

780
00:37:55,220 --> 00:37:55,940
Right?

781
00:37:56,860 --> 00:37:57,540
Yes.

782
00:38:02,220 --> 00:38:03,300
Go to the kitchen

783
00:38:03,300 --> 00:38:04,580
and get me whatever delicate snacks

784
00:38:04,580 --> 00:38:05,500
you can find.

785
00:38:06,100 --> 00:38:07,500
Put them in the red wooden basket

786
00:38:07,500 --> 00:38:08,340
inlaid with shells.

787
00:38:13,820 --> 00:38:15,420
His Majesty gave me a vase.

788
00:38:16,740 --> 00:38:18,860
I’ll prepare something to eat

789
00:38:19,140 --> 00:38:20,140
and say thank you to him.

790
00:38:22,540 --> 00:38:23,340
Aye.

791
00:38:26,980 --> 00:38:28,980
We have the plan

792
00:38:28,980 --> 00:38:31,540
because Yelv Hongji sneaked into the Capital.

793
00:38:31,860 --> 00:38:33,180
But I don’t think

794
00:38:33,660 --> 00:38:35,860
we should transfer

795
00:38:35,860 --> 00:38:37,940
Ouyang Xiu, Cai Xiang, Han Qi and Fu Bi

796
00:38:37,940 --> 00:38:39,020
back to the Capital.

797
00:38:39,620 --> 00:38:41,460
Seems like no local officials

798
00:38:41,940 --> 00:38:43,820
are able to help you, Your Majesty.

799
00:38:45,180 --> 00:38:47,580
You certainly can help me.

800
00:38:50,620 --> 00:38:52,820
The crown prince of Khitan came to the Capital,

801
00:38:52,820 --> 00:38:53,740
in the name of someone else.

802
00:38:54,620 --> 00:38:56,740
It’s against the convention.

803
00:38:57,260 --> 00:38:59,700
But you still need to investigate

804
00:38:59,940 --> 00:39:02,420
if he is up to something

805
00:39:02,420 --> 00:39:03,380
and take precautions.

806
00:39:04,060 --> 00:39:06,780
This is about our nation.

807
00:39:07,500 --> 00:39:08,380
So,

808
00:39:08,780 --> 00:39:10,300
I’ll let Ouyang Xiu and Cai Xiang

809
00:39:10,300 --> 00:39:12,740
to take care of less important things

810
00:39:13,100 --> 00:39:14,220
like holding banquets

811
00:39:14,260 --> 00:39:15,740
or enjoying performances.

812
00:39:16,540 --> 00:39:17,980
It’s been days

813
00:39:18,180 --> 00:39:20,020
since I saw Cai Xiang’s handwritings

814
00:39:20,220 --> 00:39:21,940
or read Ouyang Xiu’s good articles.

815
00:39:24,460 --> 00:39:25,620
His Majesty is at a meeting.

816
00:39:27,180 --> 00:39:28,820
I’ll just wait here.

817
00:39:33,380 --> 00:39:35,660
Your Majesty, you look tired.

818
00:39:36,100 --> 00:39:40,380
Why don’t we carefully check

819
00:39:40,580 --> 00:39:43,020
Yelv Hongji’s schedule in the past one year

820
00:39:43,180 --> 00:39:45,460
and see if there’s anything fishy

821
00:39:45,780 --> 00:39:48,780
before we report for further discussion?

822
00:39:48,860 --> 00:39:49,740
What do you think?

823
00:39:50,380 --> 00:39:51,380
Good idea.

824
00:39:52,140 --> 00:39:54,540
I’m a bit tired.

825
00:40:16,260 --> 00:40:17,900
Do you like them?

826
00:40:21,460 --> 00:40:22,940
You bring the snacks to me personally.

827
00:40:23,440 --> 00:40:24,500
I like them, without doubt.

828
00:40:27,540 --> 00:40:29,460
Your Majesty, you gave me a vase.

829
00:40:30,420 --> 00:40:32,820
But I don’t have anything

830
00:40:32,820 --> 00:40:34,260
to return you.

831
00:40:35,780 --> 00:40:36,820
I can only take care of you

832
00:40:36,820 --> 00:40:38,060
as much as I can.

833
00:40:40,340 --> 00:40:41,140
But...

834
00:40:43,220 --> 00:40:44,460
I wonder

835
00:40:44,580 --> 00:40:46,180
if you’re still angry with me.

836
00:40:51,180 --> 00:40:53,340
When was I truly angry with you?

837
00:40:54,780 --> 00:40:56,100
You kicked me away

838
00:40:56,580 --> 00:40:57,740
more than once.

839
00:40:58,820 --> 00:41:00,580
But you lost temper,

840
00:41:00,580 --> 00:41:01,540
and smashed my vase.

841
00:41:04,020 --> 00:41:04,900
Well,

842
00:41:06,100 --> 00:41:07,020
I explained very clearly

843
00:41:07,020 --> 00:41:08,020
why I did so

844
00:41:08,020 --> 00:41:08,980
that day.

845
00:41:10,660 --> 00:41:12,180
I don’t want to explain again.

846
00:41:13,660 --> 00:41:15,300
Nor do I want to get on with you like that.

847
00:41:16,460 --> 00:41:17,740
If you still don’t understand,

848
00:41:18,780 --> 00:41:19,740
I won’t push you.

849
00:41:21,340 --> 00:41:22,660
Take your time to calm down

850
00:41:23,740 --> 00:41:24,540
and think carefully about it.

851
00:41:35,530 --> 00:41:36,540
I already understand.

852
00:41:39,180 --> 00:41:39,980
So...

853
00:41:49,860 --> 00:41:51,060
So, here I am.

854
00:41:53,820 --> 00:41:55,500
To thank you for your gift,

855
00:41:58,140 --> 00:41:59,100
and beg you

856
00:42:02,380 --> 00:42:03,180
to forgive me.

857
00:42:05,260 --> 00:42:06,060
Please do not

858
